  "text": "In contrast to Gag and Env, no mature Pol subunits (>50-fold reduced) were detectable in particle preparations of the Gag ΔGR and GR R/A mutants. Only released Pol precursor was detected in the samples, which was readily digested by subtilisin and was therefore not particle-associated ( Figure 3B , lane 2, 3, 9, 10) as demonstrated previously [CITATION_1] .",
