    "14260933": {
      "title": "Orthoretroviral-like Prototype Foamy Virus Gag-Pol expression is compatible with viral replication",
      "abstract": "Background ::: Foamy viruses (FVs) unlike orthoretroviruses express Pol as a separate precursor protein and not as a Gag-Pol fusion protein. A unique packaging strategy, involving recognition of briding viral RNA by both Pol precursor and Gag as well as potential Gag-Pol protein interactions, ensures Pol particle encapsidation."
